To renew the SSL Certificate, follow:
1. Download (.csr) file from (libreq) server.
2. Send the above (.csr) file to r.milne@rgu.ac.uk. Sample emeil:
--------------
Hi Richard,
Please find attached a new certificate signing request. Please get the signed certificate back to me as soon as you can so we can get it updated.
In case of any further questions, please let me know.
---------------
3. They will send you back two files (.pem) and (.cer). Download them. I had a problem with downloading the (.cer) file. I think this is a security reason. I asked Scott to manually change extension from (.cer) to (.pem) and it worked.
4. Upload both the files to (libreq) server and send a standard UniDesk call to ITI Team.
